sentences: Parson James (born June 7, 1994) is an American singer and songwriter.
On February 5, 2016, he released his extended play release The Temple EP on Sony Music with a full studio album due later on RCA Records.
James signed with RCA Records in early 2015 after the release of his first single, "Stole the Show", a collaboration he co-wrote with Kygo.
